'''''Carpacoce''''' is a [[genus]] of [[flowering plant]]s in the [[Family (biology)|family]] [[Rubiaceae]].<ref>[https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/699857#page/38/mode/1up Sonder, Otto Wilhelm in W.H.Harvey et al. 1865. Flora Capensis; being a systematic description of the plants of the Cape Colony, Caffraria, & port Natal. London, p 32-33]</ref> All species are [[Endemism|endemic]] to the [[Cape Floristic Region]] of [[South Africa]].<ref name="WCSP">{{cite web|url=http://apps.kew.org/wcsp/qsearch.do?plantName=Carpacoce|title=''Carpacoce'' in the World Checklist of Rubiaceae|accessdate=June 2014}}</ref>

==Species==
*''[[Carpacoce burchellii]]'' <small>Puff</small>
*''[[Carpacoce curvifolia]]'' <small>Puff</small>
*''[[Carpacoce gigantea]]'' <small>Puff</small> (apparently extinct)
*''[[Carpacoce heteromorpha]]'' <small>(H.Buek) Bolus</small>
*''[[Carpacoce scabra]]'' <small>([[Carl Peter Thunberg|Thunb.]]) [[Otto Wilhelm Sonder|Sond.]]</small>
**''Carpacoce scabra'' subsp. ''rupestris'' <small>Puff</small>
**''Carpacoce scabra'' subsp. ''scabra'' 
*''[[Carpacoce spermacocea]]'' <small>([[Heinrich Gottlieb Ludwig Reichenbach|Rchb.]] ex [[Curt Polycarp Joachim Sprengel|Spreng.]]) [[Otto Wilhelm Sonder|Sond.]]</small> 
**''Carpacoce spermacocea'' subsp. ''orientalis'' <small>Puff</small>
**''Carpacoce spermacocea'' subsp. ''spermacocea'' 
*''[[Carpacoce vaginellata]]'' <small>Salter</small>

